HEADWORD: 7
<hw>7</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>One more than six; constituting or
denoting a quantity consisting of seven items or units; -- representing
the number seven as an Arabic numeral</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> seven, vii</syn>⟦br⟧
